This project evaluates data-analysis agents on the InfiAgent-DABench (DAEval)
benchmark.

Benchmark: InfiAgent-DABench: Evaluating Agents on Data Analysis Tasks (ICML 2024)
Authors:   Xueyu Hu et al.
Code:      https://github.com/InfiAgent/InfiAgent  (examples/DA-Agent)
Paper:     https://arxiv.org/abs/2401.05507
Data license: CC BY-NC 4.0 (non-commercial). The DAEval questions, labels, and
              CSV tables under data/daeval/ are redistributed for non-commercial
              research use under that license and remain (c) their authors.

data/daeval/OFFICIAL_eval_closed_form.py is the authors' original evaluation
script, kept verbatim as a faithful reference for comparability. Our verifier
(src/da_verify/tasks/verifier.py) is an independent re-implementation that is
byte-compatible with it by default and documents every deliberate divergence.

